{"title":"Leetcode第34题：在排序数组中查找元素的第一个和最后一个位置","slug":"2019101501","date":"2019-10-15T10:32:23.000Z","updated":"2019-10-15T10:40:58.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019101501.json","excerpt":"题目给定一个按照升序排列的整数数组 nums，和一个目标值 target。找出给定目标值在数组中的开始位置和结束位置。","covers":["https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hbb1846780d8c49fb96e0559516006bd33.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hac456df3b3b2496097518203dcd6ecfaO.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"题目\"><a href=\"#题目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目\"></a>题目</h2><p>给定一个按照升序排列的整数数组 nums，和一个目标值 target。找出给定目标值在数组中的开始位置和结束位置。<a id=\"more\"></a><br>你的算法时间复杂度必须是 O(log n) 级别。<br>如果数组中不存在目标值，返回 [-1, -1]。<br><strong>示例 1:</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> nums = [5,7,7,8,8,10], target = 8<br><strong>输出:</strong> [3,4]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例 2:</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> nums = [5,7,7,8,8,10], target = 6<br><strong>输出:</strong> [-1,-1]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] searchRange(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] nums, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> target) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>,b=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>,j=nums.length-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=j;i++,j--)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(a==-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[i]==target)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        a=i;i--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    i--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(b==-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[j]==target)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        b=j;j++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    j++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(a!=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>&amp;&amp;b!=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] result=&#123;a,b&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hbb1846780d8c49fb96e0559516006bd33.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>该题和<a href=\"https://www.thzone.cn/20191014/2019101401/\">第33题</a>的解决思路很像，不同之处在于，你需要再取一次“LastIndexOf”，为了减小时间复杂度，我将循环改为两边同时进行，分别寻找第一次和最后一次出现的索引，需要注意的是当你一方已经get到索引后便代表着他这边的遍历已经完成了，要保持他的下标不变。当两边均得到答案后，跳出循环即可。<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hac456df3b3b2496097518203dcd6ecfaO.png\"></p>\n","more":"<br>你的算法时间复杂度必须是 O(log n) 级别。<br>如果数组中不存在目标值，返回 [-1, -1]。<br><strong>示例 1:</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> nums = [5,7,7,8,8,10], target = 8<br><strong>输出:</strong> [3,4]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例 2:</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> nums = [5,7,7,8,8,10], target = 6<br><strong>输出:</strong> [-1,-1]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] searchRange(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] nums, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> target) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>,b=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>,j=nums.length-<span class=\"number\">1</span>;i&lt;=j;i++,j--)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(a==-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[i]==target)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        a=i;i--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    i--;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(b==-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(nums[j]==target)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        b=j;j++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    j++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(a!=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>&amp;&amp;b!=-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] result=&#123;a,b&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hbb1846780d8c49fb96e0559516006bd33.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>该题和<a href=\"https://www.thzone.cn/20191014/2019101401/\">第33题</a>的解决思路很像，不同之处在于，你需要再取一次“LastIndexOf”，为了减小时间复杂度，我将循环改为两边同时进行，分别寻找第一次和最后一次出现的索引，需要注意的是当你一方已经get到索引后便代表着他这边的遍历已经完成了，要保持他的下标不变。当两边均得到答案后，跳出循环即可。<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hac456df3b3b2496097518203dcd6ecfaO.png\"></p>","categories":[{"name":"开发","path":"api/categories/开发.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JAVA","path":"api/tags/JAVA.json"},{"name":"算法","path":"api/tags/算法.json"}]}